summary: Has Whiterun ever felt a little empty? Have you ever felt like it needed more tree's? Then you'll enjoy this mod! It adds a variety of different tree's to Whiterun!
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#ff0000][size=4]-=DESCRIPTION=-
[/size][/color][/b][size=3]This mod, in all it's simplicity add's tree's to the city of Whiterun in the most lore friendly way's possible. It aims to breathe new life into the city, by adding tree's throughout to make it a little less drab. This mod was made to work with most city mods, especially the "Dawn of Skyrim" series. The tree's added are mostly Pine and Birch, along with the odd dead tree you might find while wandering around. Enjoy the mod.[/size]

[b][color=#00ff00][size=4]-=UPDATES=-[/size][/color][/b]
[color=#d8d8d8][b] [/b]
[/color][size=3]V1 - Add's ton's of tree's to Whiterun. Very Un-Lore friendly. [OUTDATED VERSION]

V2 - Removes some previously annoying tree's, decrease city tree size and amount, tree re-positioning, more lore friendly.  
[/size]
[color=#00ffff][size=4][b]-=COMPATIBILITY=- 
[/b][/size][/color][size=3]No known compatibility issues. Especially compatible with Dawn of Skyrim collection. Please notify me if this clashes with any other mods.[/size]
